data.description: Come check out this beautiful 4 bedroom with an office and 2 bathroom home. The 5th room can work as a bedroom, study, or bonus room. It is located near shopping, Lake Hefner, and restaurants. Walk in on the wood plank tile flooring into the split kitchen, dining, and living room that boasts a beautiful brick gas fireplace with wood mantel. The kitchen has a new stainless steel dishwasher, stainless steel built in microwave,  a new BeSpoke navy steel self-cleaning convection oven with 5 gas burners and a built in air fryer with light up knobs.  The island has granite counter tops and the cabinets include a pull out spice rack and trash bin. Two bedrooms are carpeted and the other two rooms have new Pergo outlast laminate flooring with spill protector. The 5th room is wood plank tile. The primary bedroom has an ensuite bathroom with double vanity and a granite countertop, oversized walk in tile shower, and a large soaker jet tub to help you relax after a long day. The large walk in closet includes a built in dresser and shelf. The home has a New generator installed a couple of months ago to ensure you stay warm for the winter and cool during the hot summers. New water softener system was installed in 2022.  Seller's paid approximately $23k for generator and water softener alone.  The three car garage includes insulated automatic lift doors.
